OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781723470
OL,3,CCourt hears 999 call reporting
OL,4,Cstabbing of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FA court has heard a recording of the
OL,7,Fmoment a teenager called police to
OL,8,Freport a boy's claims that he'd
OL,9,Fstabbed a nine-year-old girl to death.
OL,11,FIn the recording, the girl can be
OL,12,Fheard saying to the operator:
OL,13,F"Basically, there's some kid and he's
OL,14,Fsaying that he's stabbed her and she's
OL,15,Flike dead on the living room floor,
OL,16,Fand he's ran out, and he said he's
OL,17,Fgonna get on a train to Highbridge."
OL,19,FShe tells the operator she's making
OL,20,Fthe call from Worle train station.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
