PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781723470
OL,3,CCourt hears 999 call reporting
OL,4,Cstabbing of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FThe girl then tells the operator she
OL,7,Fcan't see any visible blood on the
OL,8,Falleged attacker, before confirming
OL,9,Fthat police have arrived at the scene.
OL,11,FAria Thorpe died of a single knife
OL,12,Fwound to the heart at her home in
OL,13,FWeston-super-Mare just before
OL,14,FChristmas last year.
OL,16,FThe witness was part of a group of
OL,17,Fyoungsters at a nearby train station
OL,18,Fwho say the boy told them he had
OL,19,Fstabbed Aria by accident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
