PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781723470
OL,3,CCourt hears 999 call reporting
OL,4,Cstabbing of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FPolice arrested the boy on board a
OL,7,Ftrain as it began to leave the
OL,8,Fplatform.
OL,10,FA 16-year-old boy is on trial accused
OL,11,Fof stabbing the schoolgirl in the
OL,12,Fchest at a house in Weston-super-Mare,
OL,13,FNorth Somerset on 15 December 2025.
OL,15,FThe teenager, who was 15 at the time,
OL,16,Fdenies her murder and manslaughter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
