PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781723470
OL,3,CCourt hears 999 call reporting
OL,4,Cstabbing of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FThe court has previously heard that
OL,7,Fafter Aria was fatally stabbed, the
OL,8,Fdefendant left the house and went to a
OL,9,Fnearby railway station, telling
OL,10,Fchildren gathered there he had stabbed
OL,11,Fa child.
OL,13,FThe teenager, who cannot be identified
OL,14,Ffor legal reasons, was arrested
OL,15,Fminutes later sitting on the floor of
OL,16,Fa carriage of a train waiting to leave
OL,17,Fthe station.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
