OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781723470
OL,3,CCourt hears 999 call reporting
OL,4,Cstabbing of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination found Aria
OL,7,Fhad suffered a single stab wound to
OL,8,Fthe chest and would have "died very
OL,9,Fswiftly from her injury". The trial
OL,10,Fcontinues.
